uint16_t cvmx_pki_tag_sec::dst

Secret for the destination tuple tag CRC calculation.

Typically identical to DST6 to insure tagging is symmetric between source/destination flows.

uint16_t cvmx_pki_tag_sec::dst6

Secret for the destination tuple IPv6 tag CRC calculation.

Typically identical to SRC6 to insure tagging is symmetric between source/destination flows. Typically different from DST for maximum security.

Secret for the source tuple tag CRC calculation.

uint16_t cvmx_pki_tag_sec::src6

Secret for the source tuple IPv6 tag CRC calculation.

Typically different from SRC for maximum security.
